---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { REPLY_EMAIL } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now">
  <article class="page">
    <h1 class="font-display">Now</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated June 2026</p>
    <p>
      Right now I'm reading more than I'm writing — mostly about how large
      language models hold on to information and where they lose it, and what
      statistics has to say about the gap.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm slowly drafting a few essays that have been steeping for a while, and
      rebuilding this site so the writing has a quiet place to live without
      metrics shouting over it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Away from the screen I'm trying to read on paper again. If any of this
      overlaps with what you're working on, <a href={`mailto:${REPLY_EMAIL}`}
      >reply by email</a> — I'd like to hear about it.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
